    "description": "The RF-7800W (-OUxxx and -RPxxx) Broadband Ethernet Radio (BER) is designed for High Capacity Line of Sight (HCLOS) networks with broadband Ethernet requirements. The radio can be mounted on a mast for quick deployment or on a tower system and is designed for long haul backbone systems. The BER operates in the 4.4-5.8 GHz frequency band. The BER is an ideal wireless networking solution for public safety, first responders, training and simulation networks and long haul / short haul battlefield communications. The RF-7800W operates in Point-to-Point and Point-to-Multipoint in the same platform.",
